1.17
log
@
bye-bye libc_r sources.
the sources have been moved (with history) to /usr/src/lib/libpthread
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: pthread.h,v 1.16 2002/02/17 19:42:24 millert Exp $	*/

/*
